<div class="title">Trip to Hell</div>
<div class="substance">2C-T-2 & Methamphetamine</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=LoomingDelusion&Exact=1">LoomingDelusion</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; LoomingDelusion. "Trip to Hell: An Experience with 2C-T-2 & Methamphetamine (exp19854)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jan 3, 2003. erowid.org/exp/19854</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
